Only the elder and the younger.

38
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,420
Uncle, please hold the funeral ceremony.

39
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:29,860
I'm a prince with foreign last name.

40
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:31,180
I'm not allowed to enter the royal tombs.

41
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:32,659
Uncle.

42
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:36,659
Zhao Teng.

43
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,100
I'm here.

44
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:40,780
I grant my uncle the sword and the golden battle-axe.

45
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:43,140
From now on, uncle, you don't need to report things with your title.

46
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:44,700
You don't have to walk to the court.

47
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:46,260
You may wear your sword in the hall.

48
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:58,580
Thank Your Majesty for your kindness.

49
00:04:59,170 --> 00:05:00,220
I don't need

50
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:01,340
these extraneous things.

51
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:02,740
Uncle.

52
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:06,220
Your Majesty, take care.

53
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:28,820
In the fourth year of Shunchang, the emperor passed away.

54
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:31,460
At the age of six, the Crown Prince was crowned.

55
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:52,220
Kneel down.

56
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:57,580
Halloo!

57
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,380
Long live the emperor!

58
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:02,420
Halloo!

59
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,100
Long live the emperor!

60
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:07,300
Again!

61
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,500
Long live the emperor!

62
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,780
Pay homage!

63
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:19,740
[Xianyang Hall]

64
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:19,740
I know

65
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,260
there has always been a burden in your heart

66
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:24,860
since the late emperor was alive, Cui.

67
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:30,820
This is the royal decree for the engagement of the Crown Princess.

68
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:35,020
Cui, this is a great joy.

69
00:06:35,220 --> 00:06:37,380
Cui, accept the royal decree.

70
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:41,820
When the late emperor granted the marriage,

71
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:43,620
His Majesty was the Crown Prince

72
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:46,380
and the young lady of Cui family would be the Crown Princess.

73
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:49,300
Now that His Majesty is the emperor,

74
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:52,980
I think the young lady of Cui family should be the empress.

75
00:06:53,260 --> 00:06:54,700
This decree

76
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:55,860
is wrongly made.

77
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:59,780
