78
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:01,460
not the empress.

79
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:03,820
You don't have to be so aggressive, Cui.

80
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:06,460
His Majesty's accession to the throne is a celebration for all the country.

81
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:09,060
How about the royal family and the Cui family

82
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:11,060
each take a step back?

83
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,500
We've already made our concessions.

84
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:16,620
What more do you want, Cui?

85
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,780
I dare to ask.

86
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:22,580
His Majesty is only six years old.

87
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:24,060
How can there be a crown prince?

88
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:26,500
Isn't this decree

89
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:29,620
invalid?

90
00:07:29,700 --> 00:07:30,980
Please be at ease, Cui.

91
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:32,540
The crown prince is here.

92
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:44,580
Zixing is here to see Your Majesty.

93
00:07:44,659 --> 00:07:46,980
And Your Highness.

94
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:50,620
Get up.

95
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:53,420
Thank you, Your Majesty.

96
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:04,260
This is the third son of Prince of Wuyan.

97
00:08:04,380 --> 00:08:05,340
Liu Zixing.

98
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:06,140
From now on,

99
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:07,260
he will stay long in the palace

100
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:08,940
as His Majesty's course company.

101
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:11,340
When he reaches twenty years old, he will be the crowned Prince.

102
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:12,300
Cui,

103
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:15,900
are you satisfied with this Crown Prince?

104
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:27,820
Grand Mentor.

105
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:31,460
It's better to have this decree than without it.

106
00:08:43,860 --> 00:08:47,700
Thank you, Your Majesty.

107
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:05,060
[De'an Hall]

108
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:08,420
Take them all away.

109
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:09,540
Yes.

110
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:15,740
Be careful.

111
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:16,300
Stop!

112
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:20,660
Stop!

113
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:21,980
Your Highness.

114
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:30,060
The Empress Dowager Gao family has been executed.

115
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:38,980
[Years later]

116
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:48,540
That's a big family.

117
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,580
The Cui family is the leader

118
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:51,660
of all the clans north of the river.

119
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:52,940
Our dynasty's title was

120
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:53,620
decided

121
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:54,620
after Cui

122
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:55,780
proposed it to the emperor at that time.

123
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:58,380
That's powerful.

124
00:09:58,380 --> 00:09:59,860
That's right.

125
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:05,380
Stop the carriage.

126
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:31,540
You didn't have your lunch?

127
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:37,060
[Cui Feng]

128
00:10:34,020 --> 00:10:35,860
He's the one who gave up his royal last name

129
00:10:35,980 --> 00:10:37,420
to lead troops and protect the country.

130
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:38,500
Don't you want to see him

131
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:40,020
by this?

132
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:42,620
You already told me.

133
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:44,180
He has fought all over the country as a teen

134
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:45,780
and never lost a battle.

135
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:46,780
Don't you feel curious

136
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:48,500
about such a man?

137
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:50,540
You also told me.

138
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:52,260
He had many other

139
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,500
famous battles.

140
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:54,820
Flooding Jiang State.

141
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:56,020
The fierce battle of Shuo State.

142
00:10:56,140 --> 00:10:57,260
Six battles in Dai State.

143
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:59,380
These are all great battles that can be written in the military books

144
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:01,020
and remembered for generations to come.

145
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,620
All right.

146
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:06,220
I've said all of them.

147
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:08,860
You don't want to leave the family.

148
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,060
As your elder brother, I understand.

149
00:11:10,220 --> 00:11:11,980
So I stay and join the army

150
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:13,500
to accompany you.

151
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:15,740
Father has already agreed.

152
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:18,060
I don't have to inherit the family business anyway.

153
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:18,700
If I can stay

154
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:20,540
under the command of Jr. Prince of Nanchen to toughen myself,

155
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:23,020
I'm sure there's no reason for Father to disagree.

156
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:25,260
Now you feel happy?

157
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:28,900
Simple girl.

158
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:39,620
[Western State]

159
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:51,860
[Western State]

160
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:02,100
I'm Zhou Tianxing. Greetings to you two.

161
00:12:03,260 --> 00:12:04,540
Cui Shou from the Cui family.

162
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:05,740
This is the young lord.

163
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:08,700
We've won a great victory at the border.

164
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,340
Master has returned to the city.

165
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:11,580
He will arrive tomorrow.

166
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,580
All distinguished guests,

167
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,900
please follow me back to the royal mansion.

168
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:15,140
The clan chief has orders

169
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:15,860
that we should all stay at the post

170
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:17,260
before paying respect to the master.

171
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,020
We won't need to bother you, General Zhou.

172
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:19,900
But

173
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,620
Master ordered this in person.

174
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:22,940
It's just a couple of days.

175
00:12:23,100 --> 00:12:23,700
General Zhou.

176
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:25,540
Let's go to the posthouse first.

177
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:28,060
All right, please.

178
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:28,780
Let's go.

179
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:29,940
Let's go.

180
