193
00:13:04,340 --> 00:13:05,420
We won't disturb them.

194
00:13:05,540 --> 00:13:07,140
We'll just watch from the city from afar.

195
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:12,100
At dawn,

196
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,140
