199
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:15,740
I'm the one who takes you there.

200
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:18,380
Thank you, General Zhou.

201
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:20,100
I'll take my leave now.

202
00:13:20,380 --> 00:13:21,300
Take care, General.

203
