212
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,020
Who is it?

213
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:46,060
Don't be afraid.

214
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:49,180
This is General Zhou's token.

215
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,460
He allows us to go up to the city tower

216
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:52,140
